{{Infobox football club | clubname = Al-Shabab SC | image = | fullname = Al-Shabab Sports Club | nickname = | founded = 1962 | ground = Raqqa Stadium, [[Raqqa]] | capacity = 15,000 | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Syrian League 1st Division]] | position = | pattern_la1=|pattern_b1=|pattern_ra1=| leftarm1=|body1=|rightarm1=|shorts1=|socks1=| }}
'''Al-Shabab Sports Club''' ({{Lang-ar|'''نادي الشباب الرياضي'''}}) is a [[Syria]]n [[association football|football]] club based in [[Raqqa]]. It was founded in 1962.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.kooora.com/?team=2048|title=الشباب - Al-Shabbab|language=Arabic|access-date=22 October 2017}}</ref> They play their home games at the Raqqa Stadium.
