{{Infobox national beach handball team | Name = Norway | Badge = Flag of Australia.svg | Association = [[Australian Handball Federation]] | Coach = Boris Mensing | gender = f | World Games apps = 2 | World Games first = 2013 | World Games best = 3rd ([[Beach handball at the 2013 World Games|2013]] | World cup apps = 4 | World cup first = 2012 | World cup best = 8th ([[2012 Beach Handball World Championships|2012]], [[2016 Beach Handball World Championships|2016]]) }} The '''Australia women's national beach handball team''', also known as the Aussie Beach Gliders is the national team of [[Australia]]. It is governed by the [[Australian Handball Federation]] and takes part in international [[beach handball]] competitions.
The Women's Australian team is preparing for the World Games 2017 in Wroclaw (Poland) in July 2017..
