'''Hamitköy Spor Kulübü''' is a [[Turkish Cypriot]] [[soccer|football club]] based in [[Hamitköy]], [[Nicosia District]].<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesn/ncypclubs.html  rsssf.com]</ref>

==Colors==
The club colors are [[red]] and [[black]].<ref>[http://www.futbollogo.com/takim.php?id=309 futbollogo.com]</ref>

==Stadium==
The club's home stadium is Hamitköy Stadyumu.

