'''Tishreen Sports Club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي تشرين الرياضي}}) is a [[Syria]]n football club based in [[Latakia]].  The club was founded in 1947.

The word ''Teshrin'' in Arabic means October or November. To distinguish between the two months, it is usually referred as First Teshrin for the month of October and Second Teshrin for month of November.

